Package org.anchoranalysis.feature.io.results

Class ResultsWriterOutputNames

Object
ResultsWriterOutputNames
public class ResultsWriterOutputNames
extends Object
The customizable output names used by ResultsWriter, which all follow a pattern based on a prefix.

The group and aggregated outputs can be toggled on and off.

Author:
Owen Feehan
